  "implementation_notes": [
    "Vertical accent bar implemented as ::before pseudo-element. Fixed Figma height (132px) replaced with inset: 0; height: 100%.",
    "Action buttons use inline-alert-scoped styles, not .btn classes. Optional dependency on Button component documented in contract.md.",
    "Icon is an implementation slot. Production use should use the design system icon component.",
    "RTL uses CSS logical properties (inset-inline-start, inset-inline-end) for native RTL support.",
    "Mobile layout reflow is triggered by .inline-alert--mobile modifier or @media (max-width: 768px).",
    "Mobile close button uses position: absolute; inset-inline-end: -8px as per Figma exact value."
